email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Order Placed by Online Gateway (USER)
email_templates.subject: Order placed for Token Purchase #[[order_id]]
email_templates.message:
You have requested to purchase [[token_symbol]] token. Your order has been received and is now being waiting for payment. You order details are show below for your reference. 

[[order_details]]

Your token balance will appear in your account as soon as we have confirmed your payment from [[payment_gateway]].

Feel free to contact us if you have any questions.

email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Order Unpaid/Rejected by Gateway (USER)
email_templates.subject: Unpaid Order Canceled #[[order_id]]
email_templates.message:
We noticed that you just tried to purchase [[token_symbol]] token, however we have not received your payment of [[payment_amount]] via [[payment_gateway]] for [[total_tokens]] Token.

It looks like your payment gateway ([[payment_gateway]]) has been rejected the transaction. 

[[order_details]]

If you want to pay manually, please feel free to contact us via [[support_email]]

email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Payment Approved by Gateway (ADMIN)
email_templates.subject: Payment Received - Order #[[order_id]]
email_templates.message:
You just received a payment of [[payment_amount]] for order (#[[order_id]]) via [[payment_gateway]]. 

This order has now been approved automatically and token balance added to contributor ([[user_email]]) account. 


PS. Do not reply to this email.  
Thank you.

email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Payment Rejected/Canceled by Gateway (ADMIN)
email_templates.subject: Payment Rejected - Order #[[order_id]]
email_templates.message:
The order (#[[order_id]]) has been canceled, however the payment was not successful and [[payment_gateway]] rejected or canceled the transaction. 


[[order_details]] 


PS. Do not reply to this email.  
Thank you.

email_templates.name: Welcome Email
email_templates.subject: Welcome to [[site_name]]
email_templates.message:
Thanks for joining our platform! 

As a member of our platform, you can mange your account, purchase token, referrals etc. 

Find out more about in - [[site_url]]

email_templates.name: Send Email to User
email_templates.subject: New Message - [[site_name]]
email_templates.message: [[messages]]

email_templates.name: Password Change Email
email_templates.subject: Password change request on [[site_name]]
email_templates.message: You are receiving this email because we received a password change request for your account.

email_templates.name: Unusual Login Email
email_templates.subject: Unusual Login Attempt on [[site_name]]!!!!
email_templates.message: Someone tried to log in too many times in your [[site_name]] account.

email_templates.name: Confirm Your Email
email_templates.subject: Please verify your email address - [[site_name]]
email_templates.message:
Hello [[user_name]]! 

Thank you for registering on our platform. You're almost ready to start.

Simply click the button below to confirm your email address and active your account.

email_templates.name: Password Reset Email by Admin
email_templates.subject: Your Password is reseted on [[site_name]]
email_templates.message: We are reset your login password as per your requested via support.

email_templates.name: 2FA Disable Confirmation by Admin
email_templates.subject: Disable 2FA Authentication Request
email_templates.message:
We are reset your 2FA authentication as per your requested via support.

 If you really want to reset 2FA authentication security in your account, then click the button below to confirm and reset 2FA security.

email_templates.name: KYC Approved Email
email_templates.subject: KYC Verified: Contribute in [[site_name]] ICO
email_templates.message:
Thank you for submitting your verification request. 

We are pleased to let you know that your identity (KYC) has been verified and you are granted to participate in our token sale.

We invite you to get back to contributor account and purchase token before sales end.

email_templates.name: KYC Rejected Email
email_templates.subject: KYC Application has been rejected - [[site_name]]
email_templates.message:
Thank you for submitting your verification request. We're having difficulties verifying your identity. 

The information you had submitted was unfortunately rejected for following reason: 
[[message]]

Don't be upset! Still you want to verity your identity, please get back to your account and fill form with proper information and upload correct documents to complete your identity verification process.

email_templates.name: KYC Missing Email
email_templates.subject: Identity Verification: Action Required - [[site_name]]
email_templates.message:
Thank you for submitting your verification request. We're having difficulties verifying your identity. 

The information you had submitted was unfortunately rejected because of the following reason:
[[message]]

We request to get back to your account in order to upload new documents and complete the identity verification.

email_templates.name: KYC Submitted Email
email_templates.subject: Document submitted for Identity Verification - [[site_name]]
email_templates.message:
Thank you for submitting your verification request. We've received your submitted document and other information for identity verification.

We'll review your information and if all is in order will approve your identity. If the information is incorrect or something missing, we will request this as soon as possible.

email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Order Placed by Manual payment (USER)
email_templates.subject: Order placed for Token Purchase #[[order_id]]
email_templates.message:
You have requested to purchase [[token_symbol]] token. Your order has been received and is now being processed. You order details are show below for your reference. 

[[order_details]]

If you have not made the payment yet, please send your payments to the following address: [[payment_from]]

Your order will be processed within 6 hours from the receipt of payment and token balance will appear in your account as soon as we have confirmed your payment. 

Feel free to contact us if you have any questions.

email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Order Successful (USER)
email_templates.subject: Token Purchase Successful - Order #[[order_id]]
email_templates.greeting: Congratulation [[user_name]], you order has been processed successfully.
email_templates.message:
Thank you for your contribution and purchase our [[token_symbol]] Token! 

[[order_details]]

Your token balances now appear in your account. Please login into your and check your balance. Please note that, we will send smart contract end of the token sales. 

Feel free to contact us if you have any questions.

email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Order Rejected by Admin (USER)
email_templates.subject: Canceled Order #[[order_id]]
email_templates.message:
The order (#[[order_id]]) has been canceled. 

We noticed that you just tried to purchase [[token_symbol]] token, however we have not received your payment of [[payment_amount]] from your wallet ([[payment_from]]) for [[total_tokens]] Token.

If you still want to contribute please login into account and purchase the token again. 
[[site_login]]

Feel free to contact us if you have any questions.

email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Order Placed (ADMIN)
email_templates.subject: New Token Purchase Request #[[order_id]]
email_templates.message:
You have received a token purchased request form [[user_name]].

[[order_details]]

Order By: [[user_name]]
Email Address: [[user_email]]

Please login into account and check details of transaction and take necessary steps.


PS. Do not reply to this email. 
Thank you.

email_templates.name: Token Purchase - Canceled by User (ADMIN)
email_templates.subject: Order #[[order_id]] Canceled by Contributor
email_templates.message:
The order (#[[order_id]]) has been canceled by [[user_name]] (contributor).


PS. Do not reply to this email.
Thank you.

email_templates.name: Token Refund - Refund By Admin (USER)
email_templates.subject: Your order has been refunded
email_templates.message:
Thank you for purchase [[token_symbol]] token from [[site_name]].

We found some problem in your payment so we have refunded your order and readjusted your token balance. Please find below your refund and original purchase order details.
[[refund_details]]
[[order_details]]

Note: Your payment already refunded via same payment method that you used for payment.

If you have any questions about this refund, please feel free to contact us.

pages.title: Thank you for your interest to our [[site_name]]
pages.description: You can contribute [[token_symbol]] token go through Buy Token page. You can get a quick response to any questions, and chat with the project in our Telegram: https://t.me/icocrypto Don’t hesitate to invite your friends! [[whitepaper_download_button]]

pages.title: How to buy?
pages.description: Login with your email and password then go to Buy Token!

pages.title: Referral
pages.description:
Invite your friends and family and receive free tokens. 
The referral link may be used during a token contribution, in the pre-sale and the ICO. 

Imagine giving your unique referral link to your crypto-friend and he or she contributes tokens using your link, the bonus will be sent to your account automatically. The strategy is simple: the more links you send to your colleagues, family and friends - the more tokens you may earn!
